room_title: Escape room "Escape the Titanic" by Countdown Escape Room in Virginia Beach
room_address: 5764 Princess Anne Rd Virginia Beach, VA 23462
room_description: You and your fellow voyagers have been framed for theft by a High Society passenger. The ship is now in serious jeopardy of sinking and you are locked in one of the luxury parlor suites. You only have 60 minutes to prove your innocence by finding the missing jewelry and escape the sinking ship in the last remaining lifeboat.
